resources.string: This application allows you to turn your Wi-Fi router into a sonar.
Your phone must be stationary to use this application.
Something has been removed from the field or you have moved. New mapping required.
There is too much movement between the router and your phone to make an accurate mapping.
You must accept the permissions to use the application.
The phone is not connected to a WiFi network.
Click on the compass\nin the direction where\nthe Wi-Fi router is located.
